-- Migration: convert all TIMESTAMP columns to TIMESTAMPTZ
-- Assumes all stored values were written in UTC (the app never sets a DB timezone).
-- USING ... AT TIME ZONE 'UTC' is a no-op for UTC data but is required by Postgres
-- when casting timestamp → timestamptz.

